direction: right

Application: Application Cluster {
  style: { stroke: "#FF9900" }
}

Cloud: AWS {
  DynamoDB: lab-orders-table {
    shape: cylinder
    style: { stroke: "#3F7E44"; stroke-width: 2 }

    PK: Partition Key (PK) {
      label: "USER#123"
    }
    SK: Sort Key (SK) {
      label: "ORDER#456"
    }
    
    GSI: StatusIndex {
      label: "Query by Status\nacross all users"
      style: { stroke-dash: 5 }
    }

    TTL: Time To Live {
      label: "Auto-delete\nexpired items"
    }
  }
}

Application -> Cloud.DynamoDB: putItem / query (HTTPS)
Cloud.DynamoDB.PK -> Cloud.DynamoDB.SK: Hierarchical relation

User: Architect {
  shape: person
}

User -> Cloud.DynamoDB: Defines Schema
